	* Eris/Entity.cpp, Eris/Entity.h, Eris/TypeInfo.cpp, Eris/TypeInfo.h,
	  Eris/TypeService.h: Modify the types to store default attribute
	  data, and the Entity attributes interface to only store instance
	  attributes, and use the types for defaults.

